{"tid":1565606,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登奇蹟，震驚世界","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T11:30:25.000Z","uid":321468,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6e3c2e36f47eaa77c4c191eef190d02b302534","tid":1565606,"uid":321468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱先講吓講吓，一單又一單，就出現，就成事，就係咁誇張，就係咁豪邁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QZj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=1084b2ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g</a><br />\n<br />\n感動！震撼！新入嚟，時間太追落後，但想都2.0，3.0唔止，以下兩點在進化版或可供參考：<br />\n<br />\n1. 激昂處高潮位去到〝號角聲〞，喇叭聲不是號角聲，音樂人可否配上前置合適單音，號角聲方止歌唱聲方興，在清唱時不論何時何地，手機响起bubububu ，大家便可齊聲進入歌唱。<br />\n<br />\n2. 初聽帶歌頌/宗教感，實質好民間實況畫面，嘗試改動磨滑小小：<br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 <span style=\"color: violet;\">極</span>憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">愛</span>自由 <span style=\"color: violet;\">珍惜 這裡</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">拼</span>自由 <span style=\"color: violet;\">此刻 一鬥</span><br />\n<br />\n在晚星 墜落 徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處<span style=\"color: violet;\">輕傳</span> 號角聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也永不<span style=\"color: violet;\">斷</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 <span style=\"color: violet;\">我</span>香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">期</span>求 民主與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">美麗 明天</span> 歸香港"},{"pid":"06460d365b8719d6490d60b6f5e960ff5d9e0c5e","tid":1565606,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig